(firstQuint)Omalizumab in the Treatment of Peanut Allergy.

 The study will evaluate if omalizumab is an effective treatment for peanut allergy.

 In addition we will further evaluate the role of allergic cells (mast cells and basophils) and IgE in food allergy.

